      "rationale": "Architecture §671 + NFR-SEC-2 require that env var reads are restricted to SDLC_*, CLAUDE_* prefixes and the exact token GH_TOKEN (for pr-author specialist). Forbidden reads raise ConfigError immediately, preventing accidental credential leakage through unrestricted os.environ access."
